<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Ok, first off, there are several posts about the AGI  AC conversion...I think we all got that, thanks.  I have these on my rogue and I had banded before.  If you want AC, don't buy these.  As far as monks needing AC, I think that's funny.  If monks needed AC that bad why don't they have armor like warriors and all them other classes?  They are all about damage.  Sure that's going to aggro a lot of NPC's but that's what healers are for.  Yes, I have a monk as well.  So in conclusion, let people wear these if they want to and stop calling them stupid and clogging up the boards.  Anyways, that is my opinion.  If you don't like it, refer to the sentence 2 before this one and try to have a nice day.<BR>
<BR>
Isabelle on Brell</font></td></tr></table>
